5|$|The Haunting is a 1963 British {{psychological}} horror film {{directed and}} produced by Robert Wise and adapted by Nelson Gidding from the 1959 novel The Haunting of Hill House by Shirley Jackson. It stars Julie Harris, Claire Bloom, Richard Johnson, and Russ Tamblyn. The film depicts {{the experiences of}} a small group of people invited by a paranormal investigator to investigate a purportedly <b>haunted</b> <b>house.</b>|$|E
